title: Deployment Diagram — Physical Architecture
---
flowchart LR
    subgraph C["Client Machine"]
        BR[Web Browser<br/>React SPA + Socket.IO Client]
        MM[MetaMask Wallet Extension]
    end

    subgraph S["Server Machine (Node.js 22)"]
        EX[Express 5 Server :5000<br/>REST API + Socket.IO + Sync Engine]
        SV[Services: Merkle, Email,<br/>EventStore, Reminder Cron]
    end

    subgraph D["Database Server"]
        PG[PostgreSQL 16<br/>students, candidates,<br/>election_history, events,<br/>registration_codes, distribution_log]
    end

    subgraph BC["Sepolia Testnet"]
        AL[Alchemy RPC Node]
        E3[Election3.sol Contract]
        SG[The Graph Subgraph]
    end

    subgraph E["External"]
        PI[Pinata IPFS]
        SM[SMTP Email Server]
    end

    BR -->|HTTP :5000| EX
    BR -->|WebSocket :5000| EX
    MM -->|JSON-RPC| AL
    EX -->|TCP 5432| PG
    EX -->|queryFilter 10s| AL
    AL -->|eth_call| E3
    E3 -->|indexes| SG
    EX -->|Pinata API| PI
    EX -->|Nodemailer| SM
